definitions.definition: Pertaining to or engaging in incest .
examples: If you engaged in an incestuous relationship with a family member, that would make you an inbreeder.

definitions.definition: Characterized by mutual relationships that are intimate and exclusive to the detriment of outsiders .

main_definition: Pertaining to or engaging in incest .
